The paper deals with the problem of malware detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed scheme uses a neural network for classification, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the efficiency and resilience of the proposed scheme, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and neural networks (cs.NE).
